= class Gtk::SeparatorMenuItem

The Gtk::SeparatorMenuItem is a separator used to group items within a menu. It displays a horizontal line with a shadow to make it appear sunken into the interface.

== Object Hierarchy

* Object
  * GLib::Instantiatable
    * GLib::Object
